<DOC><DOCNO> DOE2-37-0095 </DOCNO><TEXT>A device is described for ion-beam scanning in an MI-1201 static massspectrometer synchronously with channel scanning in an AI-1024-4 amplitudeanalyzer operating in the slow-time-analysis mode. The instability ofspectrum scanning when the proposed circuit is used {le} 0.035%, whichallows a mass spectrum to be compiled in a few hours without appreciableimpairment of resolution.</TEXT></DOC>